  "keyFeatures": [
    "Enhanced note editor with Magic Key command palette and outline view",
    "Note linking with bidirectional relation tracking (inbound/outbound links)",
    "Powerful note templates with JavaScript scripting support",
    "Two-way Markdown sync with external editors like Obsidian",
    "Multi-format export: Markdown, DOCX, PDF, FreeMind mind maps, LaTeX",
    "Plugin API for other Zotero extensions to integrate",
    "Quick Note: convert annotations to notes with one click",
    "Image viewer with resize and preview support"
